#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:3
msgid "TensorCircuit: The Sharp Bits 🔪"
msgstr "TensorCircuit: 常见陷阱 🔪"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:5
msgid ""
"Be fast is never for free, though much cheaper in TensorCircuit-NG, but "
"you have to be cautious especially in terms of AD, JIT compatibility. We "
"will go through the main sharp edges 🔪 in this note."
msgstr "极致的速度并非毫无代价，虽然在 TensorCircuit-NG 中这种代价已经低得多，但在自动微分（AD）和即时编译（JIT）兼容性方面仍需格外小心。本笔记将介绍一些主要的“锋利边缘（常见陷阱）”🔪。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:9
msgid "Jit Compatibility"
msgstr "JIT 兼容性"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:12
msgid "Non tensor input or varying shape tensor input"
msgstr "非张量输入或变长形状张量输入"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:14
msgid ""
"The input must be in tensor form and the input tensor shape must be fixed"
" otherwise the recompilation is incurred which is time-consuming. "
"Therefore, if there are input args that are non-tensor or varying shape "
"tensors and frequently change, jit is not recommend."
msgstr "输入必须是张量形式，且输入张量的形状必须固定，否则会引发耗时的重新编译。因此，如果输入参数包含经常变化的非张量或形状可变的张量，则不建议使用 JIT。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:38
msgid "Mix use of numpy and ML backend APIs"
msgstr "混合使用 NumPy 和机器学习后端 API"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:40
msgid ""
"To make the function jittable and ad-aware, every ops in the function "
"should be called via ML backend (``tc.backend`` API or direct API for the"
" chosen backend ``tf`` or ``jax``). This is because the ML backend has to"
" create the computational graph to carry out AD and JIT transformation. "
"For numpy ops, they will be only called in jit staging time (the first "
"run)."
msgstr "为了使函数支持 JIT 编译和自动微分，函数中的每个操作都应通过机器学习后端调用（使用 ``tc.backend`` API 或所选后端 ``tf``/``jax`` 的直接 API）。这是因为后端必须创建计算图才能执行 AD 和 JIT 转换。对于 NumPy 操作，它们仅在 JIT 编译阶段（即第一次运行）被调用。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:54
msgid ""
"Numpy call inside jitted function can be helpful if you are sure of the "
"behavior is what you expect."
msgstr "如果您确定其行为符合预期，在 JIT 函数内部调用 NumPy 也是有帮助的。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:83
msgid "list append under if"
msgstr "if 条件下的列表附加 (list append)"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:85
msgid ""
"Append something to a Python list within if whose condition is based on "
"tensor values will lead to wrong results. Actually values of both branch "
"will be attached to the list. See example below."
msgstr "在条件基于张量值的 if 语句内向 Python 列表附加（append）内容会导致错误的结果。实际上，两个分支的值都会被附加到列表中。请参见下面的示例。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:108
msgid ""
"The above code raise ``ConcretizationTypeError`` exception directly for "
"Jax backend since Jax jit doesn't support tensor value if condition."
msgstr "上述代码在 JAX 后端会直接抛出 ``ConcretizationTypeError`` 异常，因为 JAX 的 JIT 不支持基于张量值的 if 条件。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:110
msgid "Similarly, conditional gate application must be takend carefully."
msgstr "类似地，条件门的评估也必须谨慎处理。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:145
msgid "Tensor variables consistency"
msgstr "张量变量的一致性"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:148
msgid ""
"All tensor variables' backend (tf vs jax vs ..), dtype (float vs "
"complex), shape and device (cpu vs gpu) must be compatible/consistent."
msgstr "所有张量变量的后端（tf 对比 jax 等）、数据类型（实数对比复数）、形状以及设备（CPU 对比 GPU）必须兼容/一致。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:150
msgid "Inspect the backend, dtype, shape and device using the following codes."
msgstr "使用以下代码检查后端、数据类型、形状和设备。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:162
msgid ""
"If the backend is inconsistent, one can convert the tensor backend via "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.interfaces.tensortrans.general_args_to_backend`."
msgstr "如果后端不一致，可以通过 :py:meth:`tensorcircuit.interfaces.tensortrans.general_args_to_backend` 转换张量后端。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:173
msgid ""
"If the dtype is inconsistent, one can convert the tensor dtype using "
"``tc.backend.cast``."
msgstr "如果数据类型不一致，可以使用 ``tc.backend.cast`` 进行转换。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:184
msgid ""
"Also note the jax issue on float64/complex128, see `jax gotcha "
"<https://github.com/google/jax#current-gotchas>`_."
msgstr "另请注意 JAX 在 float64/complex128 上的问题，请参阅 `JAX 注意事项 <https://github.com/google/jax#current-gotchas>`_。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:186
msgid ""
"If the shape is not consistent, one can convert the shape by "
"``tc.backend.reshape``."
msgstr "如果形状不一致，可以使用 ``tc.backend.reshape`` 转换形状。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:188
msgid ""
"If the device is not consistent, one can move the tensor between devices "
"by ``tc.backend.device_move``."
msgstr "如果设备不一致，可以使用 ``tc.backend.device_move`` 在设备间移动张量。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:192
msgid "AD Consistency"
msgstr "自动微分（AD）一致性"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:195
msgid "Gradients in terms of complex dtypes"
msgstr "关于复数数据类型的梯度"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:197
msgid ""
"TF and JAX backend manage the differentiation rules differently for "
"complex-valued function (actually up to a complex conjuagte). See issue "
"discussion `tensorflow issue "
"<https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/3348>`_."
msgstr "TensorFlow 和 JAX 后端对复值函数的微分规则管理不同（实际上相差一个复共轭）。请参阅相关讨论 `TensorFlow issue <https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/3348>`_。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:199
msgid ""
"In TensorCircuit-NG, currently we make the difference in AD transparent, "
"namely, when switching the backend, the AD behavior and result for "
"complex valued function can be different and determined by the nature "
"behavior of the corresponding backend framework. All AD relevant ops such"
" as ``grad`` or ``jacrev`` may be affected. Therefore, the user must be "
"careful when dealing with AD on complex valued function in a backend "
"agnostic way in TensorCircuit."
msgstr "在 TensorCircuit-NG 中，目前我们使这种 AD 差异透明化，即切换后端时，复值函数的 AD 行为和结果可能会有所不同，这取决于相应后端框架的原生行为。所有与 AD 相关的操作（如 ``grad`` 或 ``jacrev``）都可能受到影响。因此，在 TensorCircuit 中以后端无关的方式处理复值函数的 AD 时，用户必须格外小心。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:202
msgid ""
"See example script on computing Jacobian with different modes on "
"different backends: `jacobian_cal.py <https://github.com/tensorcircuit"
"/tensorcircuit-ng/blob/master/examples/jacobian_cal.py>`_. Also see the "
"code below for a reference:"
msgstr "有关在不同后端使用不同模式计算雅可比矩阵的示例脚本，请参阅：`jacobian_cal.py <https://github.com/tensorcircuit/tensorcircuit-ng/blob/master/examples/jacobian_cal.py>`_。另请参考下面的代码："

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:232
msgid "VMAP outside grad-like function on tensorflow backend"
msgstr "在 TensorFlow 后端将 vmap 置于梯度类函数之外"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:234
msgid ""
"Vmap (vectorized map) outside a grad-like function may cause incorrected "
"results on TensorFlow backends due to a long existing `bug "
"<https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/52148>`_ in TensorFlow "
"codebase. So better always stick to the first-vmap-then-differentiated "
"paradigm."
msgstr "由于 TensorFlow 代码库中长期存在的一个 `bug <https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/52148>`_，在 TensorFlow 后端将 vmap 置于梯度类函数之外可能会导致错误的结果。因此，最好始终坚持“先 vmap 再求导”的范式。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:237
msgid "Grad over vmap function"
msgstr "对 vmap 函数求导"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:239
msgid ""
"A related issue is the different behavior for ``K.grad(K.vmap(f))`` on "
"different backends. For tensorflow backend, the function to be "
"differentiated has a scalar output which is the sum of all outputs."
msgstr "一个相关的问题是 ``K.grad(K.vmap(f))`` 在不同后端上的不同行为。对于 TensorFlow 后端，待求导的函数具有标量输出，该输出是所有输出的总和。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:241
msgid ""
"However, for Jax backend, the function simply raise error as only scalar "
"output function can be differentiated, no implicit sum of the vectorized "
"``f`` is assumed. For non-scalar output, one should use `jacrev` or "
"`jacfwd` to get the gradient information."
msgstr "然而，对于 JAX 后端，由于只有标量输出函数才能求梯度，该函数会直接报错，它不会假设向量化 ``f`` 的隐式求和。对于非标量输出，应使用 `jacrev` 或 `jacfwd` 获取梯度信息。"

#: ../../source/sharpbits.rst:243
msgid ""
"Specifically, ``K.grad(K.vmap(f))`` on TensorFlow backend is equilvalent "
"to ``K.grad(K.append(K.vamp(f), K.sum))`` on Jax backend."
msgstr "具体来说，TensorFlow 后端上的 ``K.grad(K.vmap(f))`` 等效于 JAX 后端上的 ``K.grad(K.append(K.vamp(f), K.sum))``。"
